{"tid":510704,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，有興趣就入group行山/露營/郊遊啦!","createTime":"2017-12-26T17:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T13:39:03.000Z","uid":158199,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9e503c910e13416252b0312ec51a55bab50b394e","tid":510704,"uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"自己約係一個月前開咗個telegram group，<br />\n如果你希望可以join一個group係唔需要經常上水睇message，<br />\n間中又可以出來行下山，搵人出來吹下水，唔洗咁自閉，出去見下人，<br />\n除咗返工以外，假期可以出去行下。<br />\n我諗以下依個行山下group會幾適合你。<br />\n<br />\n本身依個group暫時都係主要搞行山，我自己搞行山活動多數都係週未，group入面都有人係週未唔得，反而平日得，所以無論咩時候先得閒行到山，只要你對行山有興趣，想搵人一齊行下山，就觀迎你入來。<br />\n<br />\n我會嘗試搞多D稍為有少少唔同的郊遊/行路活動，例如露營，或者行市區影相，但係我咁大個人係未試過路營呢!所以有玩下露營的人士都觀迎入來，甚至發起活動。<br />\n<br />\n當你發起活動後，為咗方便你，我都會加埋你做admin，所以你會見到Group入面好多Admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家諗住邀請約10至15個有興趣想搵人行山的人入group，歡迎自行發起行山/露營/郊遊/攝影團，Group內入面的人真心都唔錯，勁nice，有興趣就click以下網址啦!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HAeSJUr6vI5XvpHjoEk96A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHAeSJUr6vI5XvpHjoEk96A&d=nEtR1YQzFX9HVHqz6mdGYF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ff828e76\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HAeSJUr6vI5XvpHjoEk96A</a><br />\n<br />\n貼幾張相引下大家入來先!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/0jb4fY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F0jb4fY.jpg&h=57149998&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/jZBn83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FjZBn83.jpg&h=a3f9410a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Zv8w0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FZv8w0b.jpg&h=5cd9cb49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd27294af083c82190825670336bb9847bb95811","tid":510704,"uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T23:36:15.000Z","msg":